dc_title_s: Totivs Sveviae novissima tabvla; Amstelodami ex officina Ioannis Ianssonii.; Totius Sueviae novissima tabula
dc_creator_sm: Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664.,Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664. Atlantes Maioris Appendix, 1630.,Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. The title cartouche includes farmers with a ram and a cow. From "Atlantis maioris appendix", Johannes Janssonius, 1630. 1 map; 47 x 37 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
